--------selection/ bookmark-----------
--1. with one table---
B1:  copy table --> paste
B2: Hide table
B3: create bookmart --> unhide table --> update bookmart
B4: Insert button --> action --> link to the bookmark

--2. with more than 2 tables--
B1: Copy all tables --> paste
B2: Hide all tables
B3: create bookmark for each table:
- unhide table 1 --> bookmark 1
- hide table 1, unhide table 2 --> bookmark 2
- hide table 2, unhide table 3 --> bookmark 3
B4: Create bookmark to hide all tables: hide all tables --> bookmark "reset"
B5: Create buttons --> link to all bookmarks
